    "subject": {
      "text": "Subject: Application for Apprenticeship Opportunity"
    },
    "body": {
      "paragraphs": [
        "Dear Sir/Madam,",
        "I am reaching out to formally request an apprenticeship opportunity on behalf of {{student_name}}, a dedicated {{year}} B. Tech student majoring in {{branch_name}}. {{student_name}} is currently enrolled in the academic session {{session}} at Trident Academy of Technology, Bhubaneswar, and holds registration number {{reg_no}}.",
        "Trident Academy of Technology is proud to be affiliated with Biju Patnaik University of Technology, Rourkela, Odisha, and accredited by the All India Council of Technical Education (AICTE), New Delhi.",
        "We kindly ask for your consideration in allowing {{student_name}} to apply for an apprenticeship within your esteemed organization. The proposed duration for this apprenticeship is approximately {{duration}}, starting from {{start_date}}.",
        "We firmly believe that an apprenticeship opportunity at your organization would offer {{student_name}} invaluable hands-on experience, perfectly aligning with academic pursuits and future career aspirations. This apprenticeship is part of the academic curriculum and will contribute significantly to the student's professional development.",
        "Thank you sincerely for reviewing our request."
      ],
      "conditions": []
    },
    "signature": {
